Gaming, crafting, chatting, avatars, shows, parties, and more!
Cluster is a metaverse platform where anything is possible.
Let’s explore your new life in the virtual space!

[What is Cluster?]
A metaverse platform where users can gather and play in a virtual space from a variety of environments, including smartphones, PCs, and VR devices.
You can customize and don avatars, play and create games, and craft your own world.
Of course, you can easily communicate with your friends by text chat, voice chat, and direct message.
Let's play together in a new world!

[GAMES - Let's play games! Let's make them, too!]
There are more than 2,000 games in the virtual reality world of Cluster, and the number continues to grow.
You can enjoy games alone or play multiplayer games with your friends while talking and chatting.
Athletic games, shooting games, riddles, escape games, board games, mahjong, cards, slots, wargames, tag games, car racing, FPS, horror games, city-building simulations, and much more!
You can even create your own games and have everyone play them.

[AVATARS - Customize and change up your avatar!]
You can create your avatar and become who you want to be!
Keep your avatar up to date with the latest fashion trends, enjoy cosplay, and customize!
What kind of avatar will you create?

[CREATE - Craft with World Craft or Creator Kit]
Let's create worlds!
World Craft allows you to freely create your own metaverse space.
There are many items available, and you can easily create your world with a single smartphone.
The possibilities are endless, whether you are creating your ideal world by yourself or with your friends.

[EVENTS - Join us for virtual concerts and events!]
DJ events, live performances, festivals, talk shows, seminars, study sessions, presentations, and meet-ups with your bias!
There are a variety of fun events held every day on the metaverse! You might even find friends that you share biases with!
Join in the events where you can enjoy performances unique to virtual reality (VR) anytime, anywhere!
You can also liven up the performances with items!
Of course, you can also organize your own events - try your hand at being a singer or a performer!

[COMMUNICATE - Have fun chatting with your friends!]
You can communicate with anyone, anywhere, in various ways by voice chat, text chat, messages, and emotes!
Of course, you can also chat with a limited number of friends in a private space.
You can also take and post stylish photos, share your memories, and have fun.
Enjoy the new discoveries and friends in the metaverse space!

[Cluster is recommended for people who…]
- Are interested in the metaverse, Virtual Reality (VR), and 3D
- Want to play and create games
- Often play board games, mahjong, cards, wargames, and other party games
- Want to craft something, be it with blocks or a building sim
- Often watch virtual live-streaming of VTubers and YouTubers
- Like live music and DJ events
- Want to participate in or organize virtual events
- Enjoy talking with friends through voice or text chat
- Want to be popular in the virtual reality (VR) world
- Like dressing up and changing avatars to express yourself
- Want to explore anime-like worlds
- Are interested in Unity
- Have a VR device and want to enjoy it
- Want to be a resident of the metaverse
- Want to connect with the outside world from the comfort of your home
- Want to meet new friends

Step into your new world with Cluster!
